{"tid":1925253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習近平致電南韓、伊朗及意大利領導人慰問疫情","createTime":"2020-03-14T08:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:37:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a96087aa10db003302a0ea1adf30cdf7facfb3e9","tid":1925253,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"習近平致電南韓、伊朗及意大利領導人慰問疫情<br />\n14.03.2020 14:32<br />\n國家主席習近平致電南韓總統文在寅、伊朗總統魯哈尼及意大利總統馬塔雷拉，就近期當地發生的新型冠狀病毒疫情，代表中國政府和中國人民致以誠摯慰問。習近平指，疫情沒有國界，世界各國是休戚與共的命運共同體，唯有團結協作才能應對各種全球性風險挑戰，中方願意同國際社會攜手努力，共克時艱，早日戰勝疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n累完街坊問人死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9bde916f3a7933d808a4372ddb29de33801b3a","tid":1925253,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9bf41bd51e62524296e2cbb74e8d2b2cf11421","tid":1925253,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:45:55.000Z","msg":"中國自煮燃發，一帶一怒輸出世界。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全面實現走出去科學發展觀，落成對比式小康社會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ba2fcd39f142f756c1c403e7dd8aee5c8e9673","tid":1925253,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e29e5e2dc32e1b26a9f946d306a33f6750f9f73","tid":1925253,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"田生地產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hk